OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChancellor to abolish tax  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon period pants            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tax on period pants will be abolished  
OL,6, in the Autumn Statement, the BBC has   
OL,7, been told.                             
OL,9,FOn Wednesday, the chancellor is        
OL,10,Fexpected to announce that the underwear
OL,11,F- which is absorbent, washable and     
OL,12,Freusable - will be "zero-rated" and no 
OL,13,Flonger subject to Value Added Tax (VAT)
OL,14,Ffrom January.                          
OL,16,FOther period products such as pads and 
OL,17,Ftampons have been exempt since 2021.   
OL,19,FIt follows a campaign by retailers,    
OL,20,Fwomen's groups and environmentalists.  
